event.title: GNU Hackers Meeting, Göteborg, Sweden
event.body:
FSFE is sponsoring the international meeting for GNU hackers and contributors, in which Karsten Gerloff, FSFE President, and Adriaan de Groot, FTF Coordinator, will participate.
Place: IT University, Patricia Building, Vin Cerf Room, Forskningsgången 6, Gothenburg
Date: Wed 11 - Fri 13 November 2009 (GHM) and Sat 14 - Sun 15 (FSCONS)
On registration only
More information on GNU.org
